The '''''Tippler's Groan''''' was a commercial passenger [[Starship/Legends|starship]]. In [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]], after escaping from [[Coruscant/Legends|Imperial Center]], [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] flew on the ''Tippler's Groan'' from [[Darsie]] to [[Phorliss]].

